==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tapoa tafa
<hw>Ta*po"a ta"fa</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A small
carnivorous marsupial (<spn>Phascogale penicillata</spn>) having long,
soft fur, and a very long tail with a tuft of long hairs at the end; --
called also <altname>brush-tailed phascogale</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tappen</ent>⟦br⟧
